The paper discusses the use of automated theorem provers in extended static checking, which is a software engineering technique. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of formal verification techniques, which falls under cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). Additionally, the paper proposes using machine learning techniques to improve performance, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
